{"tid":2315062,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府: 香港是”國製金融中心”，政協成龍曾說過: 中國製的會爆炸，所以信政府 唔驚","createTime":"2020-12-07T03:22:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-07T03:34:58.000Z","uid":108201,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"adda790b15e0265217912d25ac1bb8950e2d853b","tid":2315062,"uid":108201,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:22:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zy71yAV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZy71yAV.jpg&h=444adbb2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】財政司司長陳茂波出席立法會財經事務委員會，被問到許智峯及家人戶口未經法庭批准下被凍結，有議員質疑有部門出錯，陳茂波認為指控是臆測，不會評論個別事件。<br />\n<br />\n陳茂波：「指控純粹憑臆測，我們不會就個別個案詳情在這裡進行討論，<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"red\"><strong>至於香港金融中心的地位</strong></span></span>，自去年暴力事件到今年新冠疫情，到過去幾個月所謂制裁，我們經歷過十幾個月的挑戰，仍然穩如泰山，我覺得議員的提問不需要再處理。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=415646\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415646&d=MiI%2Ba6G9rqdq%2F0stJtUYToWZOtE43EI%2FqUWggxD1P9E%3D&h=5b828427\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D415646&h=8561b0e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/local/player?newsId=415646</a>"},{"pid":"27cf399490219c0fec46dbb3d1423b15b9f177e9","tid":2315062,"uid":108201,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-07T03:34:58.000Z","msg":"今日跌得五百點，驚閪咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}